    "一个目录就是一个群。同目录的成员共享话题，无需服务器。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "One directory is one space. Members on the same directory share topics. No server."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "不可恢复，且会同步从其他设备删除。无恢复码将无法找回。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Irreversible. Will also delete from other devices via Keychain sync. You cannot recover without the recovery code."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "不可恢复：抹除此身份及其全部话题群。开启钥匙串同步的其他设备也会一并删除。请先导出恢复码。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Irreversible. Wipes this identity and all its spaces. Devices syncing the Keychain will also delete it. Export a recovery code first."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "仅切换身份，**不会删除任何数据**。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Just switches identity. **No data is deleted.**"
          }
        }
      }
    },
