    "加入后会在本机新建一个 WebDAV 绑定；可在「我的话题群」里管理。链接有效期至 %@。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Joining adds a new WebDAV binding on this device; manage it in 'My Spaces'. Link valid until %@."
