    "将从本机移除该话题群与已保存的凭据；WebDAV 服务器上的共享数据不受影响。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Removes this space and saved credentials from this device. Shared data on the WebDAV server is unaffected."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "将在本机创建群目录，之后可在设置里改为 WebDAV。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "A local space directory will be created. You can switch to WebDAV later in Settings."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "将替换本机当前身份，并恢复其全部话题群。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
